 <title>February 2015</title>
 <link>http://plus.pacenet.eu/newsletter/february-2015</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PACE-Net Plus&lt;/strong&gt; is a project funded by the European Commission to strengthen further bi-regional science, technology and innovation (ST&amp;amp;I) cooperation and dialogue between the Pacific Region and the European Union. The project brings together 16 members, from the Pacific region and the EU.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;partnerLogos&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://plus.pacenet.eu/partners/ird&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://plus.pacenet.eu/sites/default/files/logos/IRD.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
